Bullet Update:
    - Added Player Direction member to assist in bullet creation
    - Changed Bullet speed from 10 to 12.
    - Added Player delay between bullet shots
        - The player can only shoot new bullets every once in x amount of frames (currently 15)
    - Added linked list removal of bullets
    - Added Entity Collision and updates
        - Now bullets kill entities when they collide and kills itself as well.
    - Added Barrier Collision and updates
        - Bullets deactivate themselves when they touch any barrier.
